extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":10549,"user_name":"国卿 Bashᵖᵐ","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1032818,"ip_address":"","ucode":"FDC25B00489500","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/c2/72/cabfa32b.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1527591175,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"3510","content":"如果沟通无效 可以反馈 ","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"Xiaoyin","uid":"1071429","ctime":1527835403,"ip_address":"","comment_id":10549,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"27297394951","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"1.尝试积极的与此工程师一对一沟通，以提问题的方式开展对话，少说多听，听对方对于此功能的建议，抱怨，挖掘对方不满的原因。找到合适的时机阐述产品经理的思考方式，产品需求由来。也让对方明白此刻不是闹脾气的时候，每一个人都要对产品结果负责，放下杂念积极做事。<br><br>2.测试体验太差，遇到问题多考虑下内因，是否是自己没有做好走查的工作，daily build是否都去体验尽早发现问题不让工程师知道最后才进行修改。外因工程师是否是小白刚入行，对于产品的交互理解不到位，自己是否有帮助对方确认过交互逻辑。如果是自己的原因导致的，先对工程师给予抱歉，并说明自己的工作不足，并表明下一步的整改计划，产品上线后表达对对方工作配合的谢意。不论是内因还是外因，客观分析后完善自己在产品执行上的深度。如果多次沟通后此工程师并没有改善，是否可以给boss反馈换人？<br><br>3.善用自由选择，会提出两个方案，其中一个方案明显要优于另一个方案，统一对方的决策模式，让对方二选一。如果此时对方能够提出更好的建议方案，也要虚心接受，不能坚持产品经理的面子。","like_count":6,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1071429,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/59/45/a670a0b6.jpg","nickname":"Xiaoyin","note":"","ucode":"7BDEFC4D2787BF","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":418524,"discussion_content":"如果沟通无效 可以反馈 ","likes_number":1,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1527835403,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":10239,"user_name":"邹优杰","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1092397,"ip_address":"","ucode":"C4AC6921284CE7","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/ab/2d/75d45935.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1527398376,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"3262","content":"多谢 很开心你觉得有用！","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"Xiaoyin","uid":"1071429","ctime":1527495784,"ip_address":"","comment_id":10239,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"23002234856","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"这节课很有收获，实践意义很大，谢谢曲老师","like_count":5,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1071429,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/59/45/a670a0b6.jpg","nickname":"Xiaoyin","note":"","ucode":"7BDEFC4D2787BF","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":418406,"discussion_content":"多谢 很开心你觉得有用！","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1527495784,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":138367,"user_name":"向哲","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1657179,"ip_address":"","ucode":"48EA96D6B666E8","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/19/49/5b/e2d63405.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1570181385,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"14455083273","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"执行问题，我可能会找机会私下和工程师聊聊，一起吃午餐，看看最近有什么可以一起做的事情，比如打球锻炼什么的，或者看看他最近有什么难做的事情，如果有可能自己能不能稍微帮一下<br><br>沟通问题，最好的方式，就是文中说的，把背景和结果什么都说了，大家也能理解，产品把责任担了，及时站出来。看看怎么优化调整，进度和大家同步，感谢大家。如果不能调整的话，也要总结下原因，做到真诚、及时、把事弄清楚说明白。再就是，可以把决策权放在其他相关部门的手里，比如是给业务部门做得，看看他们有什么意见，用业务部门的意见作为参考。最后，较差的方案，看看老板什么意见，不上线把锅给老板。<br><br>背景问题，首先要承认技术方面确实没有人家厉害，专业的人做专业的事情，接纳自己，好的产品需要的是很多人一起的协作，而不是一个人的solo，尊重和欣赏工程师做得优秀的部分。再就是，要突出自己在用户洞察、产品、业务、数据方面的优势，技术专业方面可以尊重他们的意见，但是和用户、产品相关的部分产品也可以提出意见，技术实现出来还是给人用，优势部分尽力做到专业、靠谱。最后，信任的建立的过程是需要花时间的，第一印象很重要，注意平时工作的细节，必做得事，往专业极致的方向做。不会的事情，也要做到遇事不躲，尽力往好的方向做。","like_count":3},{"had_liked":false,"id":14098,"user_name":"Lynn","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1091151,"ip_address":"","ucode":"2BDA5F200BAF0F","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/a6/4f/295b06aa.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1530172280,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"4830","content":"同意！ ","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"Xiaoyin","uid":"1071429","ctime":1530350444,"ip_address":"","comment_id":14098,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"14415074168","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"产品经理需要让团队成员都有参与感，有每个人的思想结晶融入到产品中，而不只是任务的执行者。项目成功的概率会增大，个人的成就感以及团队的荣誉感都会不一样。","like_count":3,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1071429,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/59/45/a670a0b6.jpg","nickname":"Xiaoyin","note":"","ucode":"7BDEFC4D2787BF","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":419870,"discussion_content":"同意！ ","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1530350444,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":40440,"user_name":"文武","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1090482,"ip_address":"","ucode":"1C668730DE7348","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/a3/b2/71ab80d2.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1542619750,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"10132554342","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"Q1：首先线下单独找该工程师沟通，尽量用轻松愉快的方式沟通，拉近两个人的距离，并鼓励工程师在会上勇于发表自己的想法，同时在会上给该工程师更多的发言机会。<br>Q2：首先勇于承担责任，将产品被砍的责任扛过来；然后要带领大家复盘，总结产品可能被砍的原因，如何在后续的产品开发中避免类似的问题，失败也是一种收获。<br>Q3：不信任的原因是因为没有工程背景；所以首先做到尊重工程师的任何的意见和反馈，其次努力自学弥补自己这方面的缺陷，至少跟工程师能够用技术的语言沟通；更重要的是要在合作中体现自己的产品价值，让工程师察觉到你有很多知识是他不具备并且需要学习的；","like_count":2},{"had_liked":false,"id":26301,"user_name":"SuperSnow","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1065351,"ip_address":"","ucode":"84C89AA8083E6A","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/41/87/d26efb2e.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1537539001,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5832506297","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"如果工程师自己估计时间估少了，那怎么来申请延长时间呢?","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":17515,"user_name":"luna","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1155702,"ip_address":"","ucode":"A550256A2BAF4B","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/11/a2/76/abb7bfe3.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1532701887,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5827669183","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"这种情况，可能是因为你作为产品经理少考虑了某些情况，也可能是突然发生了一些变故，比如公司改变了策略、竞争对手突然“搞事情”。虽然这并一定是你的责任，但是这时你还是应该积极和工程师交流，主动承担责任，告诉他们：“这个赖我，辛苦你了”。<br><br>ps，少了一个字，“虽然这并不一定是你的责任”，比较复合语境？","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":15549,"user_name":"mi","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1094303,"ip_address":"","ucode":"E44F236E44CB03","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/b2/9f/8940e107.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1531282662,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"5826249958","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"老师，您工作的团队有项目经理吗？如果有的话在职权上和产品经理是怎么划分的呢？","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":10731,"user_name":"sam","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1000417,"ip_address":"","ucode":"8D48F4B9045947","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/43/e1/b7be5560.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1527679686,"is_pvip":false,"replies":[{"id":"3508","content":"嗯 有的时候没有给力的leader就得自己上！ ","user_name":"作者回复","user_name_real":"Xiaoyin","uid":"1071429","ctime":1527835366,"ip_address":"","comment_id":10731,"utype":1}],"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"5822646982","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"工程师也有leader，老师说的很多内容感觉应该是他们负责的","like_count":2,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1071429,"avatar":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/59/45/a670a0b6.jpg","nickname":"Xiaoyin","note":"","ucode":"7BDEFC4D2787BF","race_medal":0,"user_type":2,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":418582,"discussion_content":"嗯 有的时候没有给力的leader就得自己上！ ","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1527835366,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":352966,"user_name":"人间理想","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1718011,"ip_address":"陕西","ucode":"0D6A4C402D7CBD","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1a/36/fb/b480f2ac.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1659058127,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1659058127","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"老师，当你们团队的工程师肯定特别幸福😂 都在为程序员考虑","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":334390,"user_name":"Sam_Deep_Thinking","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1001152,"ip_address":"","ucode":"8E4EF6F24B821B","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/46/c0/bf880bda.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1644915542,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1644915542","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"可惜，国内有很多【不靠谱】的产品经理，从来就没有这个想法。须知，产品和研发本来就应该是一家人。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":295878,"user_name":"Eva","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1588752,"ip_address":"","ucode":"562975BA95D762","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/18/3e/10/6fbed067.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1622627632,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1622627632","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"很有用，不光对工程师，还有跟其他人相处也是一样的。敢于承担责任，互相尊重，根据对方的个性来相处，提前做好商量……曲老师真的很厉害呢！","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":285749,"user_name":"KingSwim","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1024043,"ip_address":"","ucode":"84DE14B7EB2580","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/a0/2b/efa6dc2e.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1617002097,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1617002097","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"产品是否可以问问工程师，有什么功能是他想做的（优化的)？<br>个人经历发现，很多功能由于历史原因，看起来可以用。但是往后迭代的发现根本迭代不动或者是改一次要花很多时间。工程师特别希望把这一块重新做一次。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":269128,"user_name":"PP","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2168414,"ip_address":"","ucode":"CA3B375D320075","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/21/16/5e/5f4cd8ca.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1608534702,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1608534702","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"就第一个问题而言，通常这类人的想法和思考都是很多的。他们只是缺乏一些主动性，或者还是对自己的意见不够自信，没有勇气说出来。这样来看，作为协调统筹项目组人员的产品经理，观察到此现象可以在会上机智地push他一下，让他现场表达出意见，后面就不会出现他不说也不配合的状况了。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":254576,"user_name":"Rocky","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1483150,"ip_address":"","ucode":"5FCF390BECDF9D","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/a1/8e/03aeb9df.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1603151618,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1603151618","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"关键时候承担责任，有同理心，理解工程师核心诉求","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":202267,"user_name":"Carina Cai","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1944287,"ip_address":"","ucode":"69620D97CE25B2","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1d/aa/df/aee01d59.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1585950390,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1585950390","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"以我自己的经验，<br>1. 我觉得建立一些personal connection还是很有帮助的。比方说，如果一个工程师养狗，可以稍微聊两句狗宝宝的话题；如果一个工程师喜欢户外，可以问问他周末去了哪里。这适用于所有同事，大家都喜欢和自己有共同话题的人，所以用一些与工作无关的话题可以拉近彼此距离，也比较好沟通。当然，你自己也要对同事真的关系感兴趣，而不是为了聊而聊。<br>2. 关于工作相关的内容，一对一的谈话也会很有效率，很多人可能在有多人的会议上不太喜欢&#47;不太善于&#47;不太敢于表达自己的想法，这时候一对一的谈话可以给他们更多空间。<br>3. 我认为一定要给大家credit，让大家感受到自己的付出是被认可的，对工作也会更有激情。","like_count":1},{"had_liked":false,"id":193412,"user_name":"imoling","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1049854,"ip_address":"","ucode":"9BACE03314D3BA","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/10/04/fe/f3b31bcc.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1584892065,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":0,"score":"1584892065","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"重点想讲一下第 2 点，我现在一个团队当中担任研发经理的角色，我对我下面几个研发组长有这样的一个要求，即他们在每个产品需求评审会，乃至交互评审会上必须有能力对每个需求点能够快速定位具体的技术实现，若发现实现过程有相关的风险或者是瓶颈时，能够在需求评审会上及时提出来。我当时提出一个团队文化，团队最无耻的事情，就是研发阻碍了产品经理的想象力，比这更无耻的事情，就是产品没有想象力。😂","like_count":0,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":1975403,"avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/rNbzpa6VTaXYII5W2vrvq8j8DlNEYeFlWIDTFpCo4XMHARBHW8IqIMSfzX0XJH8R5YX2jtmLpsTtnicu2uibpCbw/132","nickname":"露娜","note":"","ucode":"D21BEB25C7F324","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":263363,"discussion_content":"我认为，对于需求中的技术实现，除了研发组长评估外，研发经理也需要做评估，乃至研发总监做评估。有的小组没有能力，整个公司研发团队有能力，也不会限制产品的经理的想象力。","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1589203081,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":190563,"user_name":"老燕","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1914357,"ip_address":"","ucode":"334ED5724C59B1","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/1d/35/f5/68cef292.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1584668867,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1584668867","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"在功能的设想阶段，就应该让工程师参与进来，让他们表达意见，在此过程当中，你可以讲明自己的想法，对产品功能的设置有一个共识，这样在过程当中遇到的困难，大家会共同来面对，减少沟通的阻力。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":167904,"user_name":"Raymond吕","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1581719,"ip_address":"","ucode":"401C7BD43095FC","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/18/22/97/7a1c4031.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1577960664,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1577960664","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"项目过程由于各种变更导致的难题一般都是层出不穷，面对这些难题，本质上就是要产品经理去解决它们。<br>想想看为什么公司要设置产品经理这个角色？首先，这个角色定位就是一个沟通协调者、一个问题推动解决者。其次，才是一个小领导，当然当领导有时就要承担责任，就要给团队背锅，就要当团队的大保姆。我觉得要想把事干成，重点就是要发动群众，调动群众解决问题。所以，始终关注人的需求，从人的需求出发思考问题，安排工作和推动工作，并且会说让人爱听的“话”，是产品经理必备的思维模式和能力。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":148697,"user_name":"木木","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1486846,"ip_address":"","ucode":"2AD54B5B3F8298","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/16/af/fe/e9127277.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1573050760,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1573050760","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"感觉像是在哄孩子，循循善诱，忍而不发。","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":117297,"user_name":"Liber","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1244231,"ip_address":"","ucode":"A5CBFDB15A7745","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/12/fc/47/a4be64d8.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1564019962,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"1564019962","product_id":100006501,"comment_content":"收了我吧，拜托😆","like_count":0},{"had_liked":false,"id":107255,"user_name":"种菜的渔民","can_delete":false,"